03:06.737 --> 03:09.372
Excuse me.

03:14.745 --> 03:16.346
Do you know her?

03:16.413 --> 03:17.764
No.

03:17.848 --> 03:19.382
Oh, God.

03:19.433 --> 03:20.750
Is that supposed
to be you?

03:20.801 --> 03:22.435
Ah, she's talented.

03:22.520 --> 03:24.604
Twisted, but talented.

03:24.689 --> 03:26.606
Why would anyone draw
something like that?

03:26.691 --> 03:28.058
Well, she's a teenager.

03:28.109 --> 03:29.476
Isn't that what they do?

03:29.560 --> 03:32.428
Play depressing music, and think
about how everything sucks,

03:32.480 --> 03:35.115
and then try and make everyone
else as miserable as they are.

03:35.199 --> 03:36.149
It's a stage.

03:36.233 --> 03:37.867
Stage or not,
that's creepy.

03:37.935 --> 03:39.035
<i>Hey, look out!</i>

03:42.707 --> 03:43.707
<i>Get those people back!</i>

